snippet.textDisplay:
Wow, i am speechless. 
This is Sufi ideology at its best. Totally captivating verses. This is the reason why I love coke Studio Pakistan,  all praises to the producer and composers. I cant explain enough on how beautiful this is. 
Referencing christianity, islam and hinduism in this poem. This is true melting pot of cultural ideals right here. 
This is required, specially when hindu muslim sentiments are tense all the time. Let the world know “arab yaar tera basant banayao, rakhiyo jagat mai laal gulaal” Beautiful.
